VAR _week = SELECTEDVALUE(Dim_Calendar_FligtDate[WeekOfYear])
 
-- handle no selection

VAR _hasSel = NOT (ISBLANK(_year) || ISBLANK(_week))
 
-- last week’s year/week (handles week = 1 → previous year’s last week)

VAR _prevYear =

    IF(_week = 1, _year - 1, _year)
 
VAR _prevWeek =

    IF(

        _week = 1,

        CALCULATE(

            MAX(Dim_Calendar_FligtDate[WeekOfYear]),

            Dim_Calendar_FligtDate[YR] = _year - 1

        ),

        _week - 1

    )
 
RETURN

IF(

    NOT _hasSel,

    BLANK(),

    CALCULATE(

        SUM(Fact_ActualFlights[UpliftVol]),

        Dim_Calendar_FligtDate[YR] = _prevYear,

        Dim_Calendar_FligtDate[WeekOfYear] = _prevWeek

    )

)
